textDelta: What food commodity is getting more popular as urbanization increases? As the world becomes more urbanized, the demand for food commodities that can be easily transported and stored, such as grains and oilseeds, increases.
How is Cobalt-60 made? Cobalt-60 is made by bombarding natural cobalt with high energy neutrons in a nuclear reactor.

Why does electricity travel faster through muscle than fat? The speed of electricity travelling through muscle and fat is determined by the resistance of the tissue. Muscle is a better conductor than fat, so electricity travels faster through muscle.
Who has the real power in the UN? The UN Security Council has the real power in the UN.
